<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Evanston</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A prairie inspired neighborhood, the Evanston real estate provides wide open spaces, walking pathways and several playgrounds, perfect for raising young children.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Complete with its dreamy meandering trails, immaculate greens and breathtaking views of the West Nose Creek that runs along the south, the community in Evanston offers abundant reasons for its residents to enjoy the idyllic outdoors of the neighborhood. </p>
